com.bigdata.blueprints

Class BigdataRDFFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.blueprints.DefaultBlueprintsValueFactory
      • com.bigdata.blueprints.BigdataRDFFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BlueprintsValueFactory

    public class BigdataRDFFactory
extends DefaultBlueprintsValueFactory
    Default implementation of a BlueprintsValueFactory for converting blueprints data to RDF and back again. Uses simple namespacing and URL encoding to round trip URIs.
    Author:
    mikepersonick
